              [wrapPrefix[n]]{request[n]}[wrapSuffix[n]]
          </body>
      </html>
 @param requests - Array of WrappedScriptRequests
 @param bufferSize - Total buffer size of all requested scripts
 @return Full URL Safe wrapped scripts
